  "info": {
    "about": "Echov redefines the modern tech retail space as the ultimate destination for premium electronics. We forged this brand entirely from the ground up—starting with a striking logo and a bold visual identity—and translated that vision into a relentless, high-performance omnichannel ecosystem. We engineered a flawless web and mobile application experience that feels effortlessly intuitive and visually cutting-edge. Our strategy was to build a digital environment where discovering, comparing, and purchasing elite tech gear is as seamless and sophisticated as the products themselves.",
    "whatWeDid": [
      "· Full Brand Strategy, Logo Design & Visual Identity",
      "· UX/UI Design for E-commerce Web & Mobile App",
      "· Custom Digital Product Development",
      "· Interaction Design & Scalable Design System"
    ],
